  profile:
    en: He arrives. He arrives at his land together with the young girl. "I'll be
      waiting. At the end of the moonlight. At the promised paradise." What is this
      promise at the end of journey? What is paradise? The curtain of the final stage
      rises. From "Performance Festival" Play - Act 6.
    ja: 'そして彼はたどり着いた。少女と共に、彼の地へ。

      「待っている。月明かりの果て、約束の楽園で」

      旅の果てに触れた約束。そして楽園の意味とは。

